{"tid":2156682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"好書推介: 撐香港科幻小說作家-吳志麗 Under the Pendulum Sun","createTime":"2020-08-14T15:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T04:33:42.000Z","uid":305173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c959f70d1c9fd07aa26cc8807c1ea1396b3d4f","tid":2156682,"uid":305173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJv2z6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJv2z6U.jpg&h=f0c3ade9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nUnder the Pendulum Sun - Jeannette Ng<br />\n<br />\n上網睇到作者得獎時啲發言就有啲好奇佢本書, 然後就開始睇<br />\n因為太好睇所以就決定po 上連登分享 <br />\n<br />\nRating: 9.5/10 <br />\n<br />\n講述主人公為咗搵阿哥而去仙國 (fae) <br />\n本書涉及左社會唔係好接受到 &amp; 比較深入嘅題材, e.g. 宗教, 亂倫<br />\n而作者巧妙地一層層咁去帶出呢D topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n故事編排得好緊湊, 好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果平時有睇開英文書, 不妨買呢本書嚟睇吓 (順便支持下作者) <br />\n<br />\nP.s. 第一次睇科幻小說, 平時睇開 articles, the economist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c83150507874061dd5e904fc6b37f5733b46e71","tid":2156682,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:45:23.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"45aa79e09a44632b5914b4e9cde1ca988e5fbb5c","tid":2156682,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"入面嘅科幻元素係咩？"},{"pid":"95773c20d8bc5e8430c00fbe878cfae650cde48d","tid":2156682,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45aa79e09a44632b5914b4e9cde1ca988e5fbb5c","tid":2156682,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"入面嘅科幻元素係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"英文"},{"pid":"7e155f31c51672de0b5721d1cca9e42c09fc8b65","tid":2156682,"uid":305173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45aa79e09a44632b5914b4e9cde1ca988e5fbb5c","tid":2156682,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"入面嘅科幻元素係咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"成個設定都好科幻, 設定於英國嘅維多利亞時代(Victorian era)主角阿哥去仙國傳教. E.g. 係故事,主角會遇到仙國皇后 (Queen Mab) <br />\n仲有好多例子, 不過廢時劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n故事背景雖然好科幻，但睇落去會發現啲題材好貼近現實生活 (不過屬係倫理灰色地帶) <br />\n<br />\n關於書名: 係仙國個太陽係搖擺不定就好似鐘擺, 所以本書會叫做under the pendulum (搖擺不定) sun"},{"pid":"6b1886fdb49483621a7b20ef74229f842f768b97","tid":2156682,"uid":305173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95773c20d8bc5e8430c00fbe878cfae650cde48d","tid":2156682,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45aa79e09a44632b5914b4e9cde1ca988e5fbb5c","tid":2156682,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"入面嘅科幻元素係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"香港人寫喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學下英文同支持返同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d005819599e588c23cc8c7d46738cd9193bb5e","tid":2156682,"uid":236099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"美國人黎下話"},{"pid":"38bac6b4365397251942797dbf3673ce328fbc23","tid":2156682,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1886fdb49483621a7b20ef74229f842f768b97","tid":2156682,"uid":305173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95773c20d8bc5e8430c00fbe878cfae650cde48d","tid":2156682,"uid":134739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45aa79e09a44632b5914b4e9cde1ca988e5fbb5c","tid":2156682,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"入面嘅科幻元素係咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:23:01.000Z","msg":"英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"香港人寫喎<img sr